# Glitch NinjaTrader boundaries

## Product scope

- The active product surface is AddOn plus Indicator.
- `ninjatrader/Glitch/Strategies` is explicit opt-in work, not part of normal maintenance or deploy scope.

## Source of truth

- `D:\click-blue\trading\glitch-platform\ninjatrader\Glitch` is the only source of truth.
- Never directly edit `C:\Users\alan\Documents\NinjaTrader 8\bin\Custom`.
- Treat `GlitchData` files as runtime state or sparse overrides, not source templates.

## Workflow

- Read `ninjatrader/Glitch/Docs/README.md`, `architecture.md`, and `persistence.md` before changing bridge, persistence, or product behavior.
- Keep AddOn and Indicator compatibility in mind when touching reflection-based bridge code.
- Finish workspace edits first. If a live deployment is needed, validate first and deploy once with the approved script.
